xml#gnd_118679236" type="Person"><lb xml:id="HANSb24413-line-00000014"/>Dehmel</rs>. <pb corresp="page/00000002.xml" xml:id="HANSb24413-page-00000002" facs="https://iiif.sub.uni-hamburg.de/object/HANSb15381/canvas/PHYS_0002"/></ab></body></text></TEI>